{"featured_counts":4,"common_counts":97,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/559609560/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=19\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/559609560/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=17\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":35},"data":[{"id":565980378,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/565980378","content":"我真的是服了，看了这么多评论都是骂提问者的，如果答主真的是个知识分子，请尊重大家的意志和智慧，中国人从众心很强，你一条评论有可能让大家都跟你一起批判提问者，从而给一个数学路上有热爱和潜力的孩子浇冷水，你真的能保证除了数学界，外行真的解不出来题目吗，数学的智慧被所谓的数学家垄断了吗？那中南大学生怎么解出来世界难题的？答案如下。进入数学界的人不会把精力放到攻克一个特定的问题上，别人要吃饭！反而业余爱好者能有这种难能可贵的勇气！\u003cbr\u003e从众心过强，导致人一边倒，可怕！","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545825552,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"56f29b56e54fd041c755b08668159d82","url_token":"ghklc","name":"ghklc","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bccba897fbcf1ac596fea091acbe9239_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bccba897fbcf1ac596fea091acbe9239_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/56f29b56e54fd041c755b08668159d82","user_type":"people","headline":"一个在新大陆上的人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":7,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":12,"child_comments":[{"id":565986579,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/565986579","content":"\u003cp\u003e你要是见过那些沉迷在自己的“理论”里面，搞得一事无成甚至家破人亡的民科，就知道你说这种话是在害人家，批判他的反而是在救他。数学的智慧当然没有被谁垄断，但如果妄想不打好基础就能摘去数学智慧皇冠，那不过是自欺欺人罢了。中南大学数学系本科生证明世界难题恰恰证明了数学的智慧没有被数学家垄断，只要你的成果能经得起检验就行。然而如果提问者真的打好了基础阅读了大量文献和前人的研究成果，他不可能连数学论文该发表在哪里都不知道，最起码发表论文的杂志怎么投稿是不可能不知道的，除非他没读过数学论文。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后我要说的是，我只是不支持提问者，并没有骂他。反而是你上纲上线，按你的意思都快把扼杀中国数学之星的罪名扣我头上了。也请你尊重科学的智慧和规律。\u003c/p\u003e","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545826431,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"45f9d9321a27227ff994f8458d59d9fa","url_token":"fishoflaw","name":"马蓝蓝","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f096591d8650bfa5d265d49724c438b_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f096591d8650bfa5d265d49724c438b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/45f9d9321a27227ff994f8458d59d9fa","user_type":"people","headline":"对闲窗畔，停灯向晓，抱影无眠。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":34,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"56f29b56e54fd041c755b08668159d82","url_token":"ghklc","name":"ghklc","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bccba897fbcf1ac596fea091acbe9239_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-bccba897fbcf1ac596fea091acbe9239_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/56f29b56e54fd041c755b08668159d82","user_type":"people","headline":"一个在新大陆上的人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":565987164,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/565987164","content":"知道你的良苦用心，如果你是这样想的，我倒是理解你，但是我更希望你把这份心也写在回答上。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545826518,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":fa